    <h1 class="article-title">How to Learn OSINT as a Beginner</h1>

    <p class="article-metadata">
      Published on 24th March, 2024
    </p>

    <figure>
		<img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/13024626/pexels-photo-13024626.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" class="article-image">
		<figcaption>
			Photo by hicret from Pexels:<a href="https://images.pexels.com/photos/13024626/pexels-photo-13024626.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" target="_blank"> https://images.pexels.com/photos/13024626/pexels-photo-13024626.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1</a>
